 width="694" height="316" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-06-at-5.23.13-PM-1-694x316.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-06-at-5.23.13-PM-1-1280x582.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-06-at-5.23.13-PM-1-768x349.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-06-at-5.23.13-PM-1-1536x699.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-06-at-5.23.13-PM-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft Store 總經理 Giorgio Sardo 於網誌中表示，「新功能可以協助用戶將以前曾下載的應用程式自動安裝在新的裝置上。」同樣地，新功能亦可以令應用程式開發商更容易地保留客戶，不需要在額外提醒下亦能令客戶繼續下載及使用其應用程式。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源： <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/microsoft/windows-11-restore-apps-feature-will-make-it-easier-to-set-up-new-pcs/">Bleeping Computer</a></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
